description:
Are you attending IBM InterConnect 2016 in Las Vegas, NV?

  • Get a head start on the others by learning the key aspects of using the IBM Events app to put together your agenda.
  • Ensure you make the most of your profile so others can easily find you.

This course is for anyone wanting to make the most of the IBM Events app prior to attending the IBM InterConnect Conference in Las Vegas.

  • I'm sharing tips I am using myself to help prepare for the conference at the end of February.
title: A developers guide to IBM Events
